id: pm-a859
title: "ADR: Config-driven runtime schema (4-file model) over hard-coded type/status/field registries"
description: Config-driven runtime schema (4-file model) over hard-coded type/status/field registries
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: adr,architecture,"area:config","area:schema"
created_at: "2026-05-31T19:47:01.768Z"
